            <lb xmlns="" n="c57-0134__main__5"/>endeavoured to alter the course of my thoughts. <lb xmlns="" n="c57-0134__main__6"/>He wished as much as possible to obliterate the <lb xmlns="" n="c57-0134__main__7"/>memory of the scenes 
        <seg th:sID="C28_app162-fMS"/>
